They're just here to help. 



My first attempt at a truly creepy skip. I hope I managed to give you all some chills, or at least some goosebumps.

Credit as due: thank you to #thecritters user PopcornK, Rounderhouse for critique!

But more importantly, thank you for reading.

Check out some of my other works here!

Note: the lack of the nu-SCP theme for this article despite all of the ones I've written before having it is intentional. I feel the regular theme fits the feel of the article better.





